Introduction

Minseo is a South Korean singer under H Music Entertainment. She is the Main vocalist and Maknae of the girl group WOOAH (formerly known as woo!ah!).

She made her debut as a member of WOOAH on May 15, 2020 with the group's first single album "Exclamation".
